# Project Structure & Architecture

This is an Electron + React + TypeScript employee performance monitoring dashboard for Dinas Sosial (Social Services Department).

## Core Architecture
- **Frontend**: React 19 SPA with Vite bundling, entry point at [index.tsx](mdc:index.tsx)
- **Backend**: Fastify + better-sqlite3 server in [server/](mdc:server/) directory
- **Electron**: Main process in [main.ts](mdc:main.ts), config in [electron-config.ts](mdc:electron-config.ts)
- **Database**: SQLite with better-sqlite3, located at [server/performance_analyzer.db](mdc:server/performance_analyzer.db)
- **State Management**: Zustand for global state, React Query for server state
- **Package Manager**: pnpm (version 10.15.1+)

## Directory Structure
- **Components**: React components in [components/](mdc:components/) - use PascalCase naming
  - [dashboard/](mdc:components/dashboard/) - Dashboard-specific components
  - [data/](mdc:components/data/) - Data management components
  - [employees/](mdc:components/employees/) - Employee-related components
  - [layout/](mdc:components/layout/) - Layout and navigation components
  - [reporting/](mdc:components/reporting/) - Report generation components
  - [shared/](mdc:components/shared/) - Reusable shared components
- **Services**: API and business logic in [services/](mdc:services/) - use camelCase naming
- **Contexts**: React contexts in [contexts/](mdc:contexts/) - use PascalCase naming
- **Hooks**: Custom React hooks in [hooks/](mdc:hooks/) - use camelCase naming
- **Types**: TypeScript interfaces in [types.ts](mdc:types.ts)
- **Constants**: Design tokens and constants in [constants/](mdc:constants/)
- **Utils**: Utility functions in [utils/](mdc:utils/)
- **Design System**: Component library in [design-system/](mdc:design-system/)
- **Server**: Fastify backend in [server/](mdc:server/) directory
- **Tests**: Unit tests in [src/__tests__/](mdc:src/__tests__/), integration tests in [test/](mdc:test/)
- **Assets**: Static files in [assets/](mdc:assets/)
- **Build Output**: Compiled files in [dist/](mdc:dist/) and [build/](mdc:build/)
- **Release**: Distribution packages in [release/](mdc:release/)

